{"title":"响亮的回答","authors":["温承训"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"响亮的回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京第一机床厂工人　温承训"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个无赖汉站在我们面前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒吼一声，暴跳三尺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊出污浊的言语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出氢弹的毒烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“贫困”哪“暗淡”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国难过1959这一关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想兴家立业又不靠“美援”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直放肆——大胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用一飞冲天的红箭头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭穿你们天大的谎言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五八年，万马飞奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五九年，五年计划两年完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人心上六亿座发射台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看：放不完的多级火箭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们红到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红在捷报上斗大的喜字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们红到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红在账本上财政的赤字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们举拳高呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大跃进的1960年！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们擦擦鼻尖上的汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连划十字在胸前："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“偏心的上帝啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别听信共产党的宣传！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}